rest_of_day_open: I will be incredibly busy planning my cross country move. Every day will involve me packing our belonging in some capacity. I will have to alert my current leasing office, our washer and drier rental company, a moving company, and all of our friends and family about the recent updated moving day.
critical_positive: Bryan (Brian?) and I had quite a bit in common. We're both currently in the South East and seem to have encountered a lot of interesting and peculiar people. We seemed to have very similar stories in regards to the shenanigans we encountered in high school. We also bonded over how much has changed during our stay-at-home orders.
critical_negative: It seemed like Bryan (Brian?) was content to talk all himself. rest_of_day_open: I have a lot of work to get done, and I have had a lot of worries about certain things at work and certain things in my personal life. But I have some really positive things that I am looking forward to, including some personal interactions (including online, but also some actual, in person activities!).
critical_positive: We had a lot of give-and-take in the conversation. What I mean is that one of us would tell a story which would trigger a memory in the other, who would tell a story or something about themselves. This would trigger another memory. I found my partner to be very personable and pleasant and friendly.
critical_negative: There was a lot we did not know about each other, but other than that, I thought everything worked well.
